<tal:block 
    define="siteName options/siteName | view/siteInfo/name | string: No Site Name;
            groupName options/groupName | view/groupInfo/name | string: No Group Name;
            groupUrl options/groupUrl | view/groupInfo/url | string: No Group URL;
            groupEmail options/groupEmail | view/groupEmail | string: No Group Email">
<hr/>
<p>To post a message, photo, file, or video to <tal:block replace="groupName"/>, log in at <a href='' tal:attributes="href groupUrl"><tal:block replace="groupUrl"/></a></p>

<p>To receive an email of every post to <tal:block replace="groupName"/>, email <a href='' tal:attributes="href python:'mailto:{0}?Subject=digest%20off'.format(groupEmail)"><tal:block replace="groupEmail"/></a> with the subject line 'digest off'.</p>
  
<p>To leave <tal:block replace="groupName"/>, email <a href='' tal:attributes="href python:'mailto:%s?Subject=unsubscribe' % groupEmail "><tal:block replace="groupEmail"/></a> with the subject line 'unsubscribe'.</p>

<p><tal:block replace="groupName"/> is hosted by <tal:block replace="siteName"/> using GroupServer and powered by OnlineGroups.Net</p>
</tal:block>
